{"id":25368,"date":"2020-02-08T11:06:02","date_gmt":"2020-02-08T04:06:02","guid":{"rendered":"\/?p=25368"},"modified":"2020-02-14T08:16:46","modified_gmt":"2020-02-14T01:16:46","slug":"huong-dan-cai-dat-wpdiscuz","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"\/wordpress\/huong-dan-cai-dat-wpdiscuz","title":{"rendered":"H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn c\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t wpDiscuz gi\u00fap h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn WordPress hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p class=\"highlight\"><strong><em>H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn c\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t plugin wpDiscuz<\/em><\/strong> \u0111\u1ec3 &#8220;th\u0103ng c\u1ea5p&#8221; h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn m\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a WordPress v\u1ed1n c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>WordPress r\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi khi t\u00edch h\u1ee3p s\u1eb5n h\u1ec7 th\u00f4ng b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn h\u1eefu \u00edch \u1edf m\u1ed7i b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn n\u00e0y kh\u00e1 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf v\u1ec1 t\u00ednh n\u0103ng v\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 WordPress kh\u00e1 &#8220;ph\u1edbt l\u1edd&#8221; trong vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfn h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn n\u00e0y qua c\u00e1c b\u1ea3n c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a WordPress.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ch\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfn nh\u1ecf \u1edf phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n WordPress 5.3 c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u00eam t\u00ednh n\u0103ng &#8220;t\u00fd hon&#8221; v\u1ec1 SEO l\u00e0 m\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ecbnh link ch\u00e8n \u1edf ph\u1ea7n b\u00ecnh lu\u00e2n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 attribute&nbsp;<code>rel=\"nofollow ugc\"<\/code>&nbsp;\u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ed1ng spam backlink m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>D\u00f9 ch\u01b0a ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o nh\u01b0ng ph\u1ea7n b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn WordPress m\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t \u1edf kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh SEO v\u00e0 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ea3i trang.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eed qua <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Disqus (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https:\/\/disqus.com\/\" target=\"_blank\">Disqus<\/a>, m\u1ed9t h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn online \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf. R\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfc, d\u00f9 kh\u00e1 th\u00edch giao di\u1ec7n v\u00e0 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 th\u00ec Disqus l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ecb c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 m\u1ea1ng ch\u1eb7n \u1edf Vi\u1ec7t Nam, bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 khi b\u1ea1n d\u00f9ng SIM 4G tr\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Quay l\u1ea1i WordPress plugin, t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t plugin b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1ng tin c\u1eady. Sau khi th\u1eed qua nhi\u1ec1u plugin, t\u00f4i kh\u00e1 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi plugin wpDiscuz mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed-wordpress wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-plugin-directory\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<div class=\"suki-oembed\"><blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"DiSiaboVy5\"><a href=\"https:\/\/vi.wordpress.org\/plugins\/wpdiscuz\/\">Comments &#8211; wpDiscuz<\/a><\/blockquote><iframe title=\"&#8220;Comments &#8211; wpDiscuz&#8221; &#8212; Plugin Directory\" class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\" src=\"https:\/\/vi.wordpress.org\/plugins\/wpdiscuz\/embed\/#?secret=DiSiaboVy5\" data-secret=\"DiSiaboVy5\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"><\/iframe><\/div>\n<\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"pk-heading-numbered\">T\u1ea1o v\u00e0 c\u1ea5u h\u00ecnh cho Form b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>N\u00f3i th\u1eadt, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 module m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n t\u1ea1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u1ebft nh\u01b0ng wpDiscuz l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 Form \u1edf d\u00f2ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. Do \u0111\u00f3, n\u00f3 s\u1ebd g\u00e2y &#8220;m\u1ea5t c\u1ea3nh gi\u00e1c&#8221; cho m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u1ea1n m\u1edbi d\u00f9ng l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image is-style-default\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/tao-form-binh-luan-wpdiscuz.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"707\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/tao-form-binh-luan-wpdiscuz.png\" alt=\"Tao Form Binh Luan Wpdiscuz\" class=\"wp-image-25384\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/tao-form-binh-luan-wpdiscuz.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/tao-form-binh-luan-wpdiscuz-218x151.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/tao-form-binh-luan-wpdiscuz-300x207.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/tao-form-binh-luan-wpdiscuz-700x483.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/tao-form-binh-luan-wpdiscuz-768x530.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>T\u1ea1o form b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng wpDiscuz<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng t\u1ea1o form n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e1, n\u00f3 cho ph\u00e9p b\u1ea1n th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 widget m\u1edbi m\u00e0 h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng m\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a WordPress kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n th\u00eam c\u00e1c ghi ch\u00fa hay h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh m\u00ecnh ho\u1ea1 th\u00ec b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u00f9ng HTML v\u00e0 Text Widget \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00e8n th\u00eam, v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ti\u1ec7n l\u1ee3i.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image is-style-default\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/tuy-chinh-form-binh-luan.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"700\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/tuy-chinh-form-binh-luan-1024x700.png\" alt=\"Tuy Chinh Form Binh Luan\" class=\"wp-image-25385\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/tuy-chinh-form-binh-luan-1024x700.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/tuy-chinh-form-binh-luan-218x149.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/tuy-chinh-form-binh-luan-300x205.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/tuy-chinh-form-binh-luan-700x478.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/tuy-chinh-form-binh-luan-768x525.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/tuy-chinh-form-binh-luan.png 1228w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tu\u1ef3 bi\u1ebfn th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tr\u01b0\u1eddng m\u1edbi v\u00e0 Layout cho Form b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Ngo\u00e0i ra, \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 n\u01a1i m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n quy \u0111\u1ecbnh wpDiscus \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t. Th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t hay &#8220;qu\u00ean&#8221; t\u00ecm \u0111\u1ebfn module n\u00e0y khi mu\u1ed1n k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn cho c\u00e1c custom post ngo\u00e0i blog.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t &#8220;quy\u1ec1n&#8221; \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn cho WordPress user role. T\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t h\u00e3y b\u1ec9 ch\u1ecdn t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 cho ch\u1eafc \u0103n.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n stick ch\u1ecdn v\u00e0o&nbsp;<code>Disable commenting for roles<\/code>&nbsp;cho&nbsp;<code>Subscriber User Role<\/code>&nbsp;s\u1ebd g\u00e2y ra m\u1ed9t v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u1edbn m\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1ng l\u00fd wpDiscus ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng. B\u1edfi v\u00ec&nbsp;<code>Subscriber User Role<\/code>&nbsp;l\u00e0 user m\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ecbnh khi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ecdc gi\u1ea3 d\u00f9ng Social login (\u0111\u0103ng nh\u1eadp b\u1eb1ng t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n Facebook, Google,&#8230;) hay \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd t\u1ea1o t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn &#8220;l\u1ea7n k\u1ebf ti\u1ebfp&#8221;.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image is-style-default\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/khong-duoc-stick-chon-trong-wpDiscuz.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"582\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/khong-duoc-stick-chon-trong-wpDiscuz-1024x582.png\" alt=\"Khong Duoc Stick Chon Trong Wpdiscuz\" class=\"wp-image-25386\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/khong-duoc-stick-chon-trong-wpDiscuz-1024x582.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/khong-duoc-stick-chon-trong-wpDiscuz-218x124.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/khong-duoc-stick-chon-trong-wpDiscuz-300x170.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/khong-duoc-stick-chon-trong-wpDiscuz-700x398.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/khong-duoc-stick-chon-trong-wpDiscuz-768x436.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/khong-duoc-stick-chon-trong-wpDiscuz.png 1317w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>C\u1ea9n th\u1eadn: B\u1ea1n n\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 nguy\u00ean nh\u01b0 h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh &#8220;block&#8221; b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn trong m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ecdc \u0111\u0103ng nh\u1eadp t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n Facebook \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tr\u00ean blog b\u1ea1n th\u00ec s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec x\u1ea3y ra, nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea7n sau b\u00ecnh ku\u1eadn th\u00ec s\u1ebd b\u00e1o l\u1ed7i v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn. T\u00ednh n\u0103ng n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t nguy hi\u1ec3m, ch\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t stick c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ecdc gi\u1ea3 b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1eefa \u1edf nh\u1eefng l\u1ea7n sau.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"pk-heading-numbered\">C\u00e1ch Vi\u1ec7t ho\u00e1 wpDiscuz<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>C\u01a1 b\u1ea3n l\u00e0 b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 2 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 vi\u1ec7t ho\u00e1 wpDiscus:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>D\u00f9ng Phrase Setting module c\u1ee7a wpDiscus<\/li><li>Ch\u1ec9nh s\u1eeda file PO c\u1ee7a plugin wpDiscus (<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"d\u00f9ng plugin Loco Translate (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https:\/\/vi.wordpress.org\/plugins\/loco-translate\/\" target=\"_blank\">d\u00f9ng plugin mi\u1ec5n ph<\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/vi.wordpress.org\/plugins\/loco-translate\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"d\u00f9ng plugin Loco Translate (opens in a new tab)\">\u00ed<\/a><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"d\u00f9ng plugin Loco Translate (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https:\/\/vi.wordpress.org\/plugins\/loco-translate\/\" target=\"_blank\"> Loco Translate<\/a>)<\/li><\/ol>\n\n\n\n<p>V\u1edbi c\u00e1ch #1 b\u1ea1n ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n v\u00e0o &#8220;Phrase setting&#8221; v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh t\u1ef1 d\u1ecbch theo \u00fd m\u00ecnh. T\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb c\u00e1c tab ch\u1ee9a c\u00e1c chu\u1ed7i ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n d\u1ecbch d\u1ec5 h\u01a1n.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image is-style-default\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/dich-wpdiscuz-sang-tieng-viet.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"508\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/dich-wpdiscuz-sang-tieng-viet-1024x508.png\" alt=\"Dich Wpdiscuz Sang Tieng Viet\" class=\"wp-image-25387\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/dich-wpdiscuz-sang-tieng-viet-1024x508.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/dich-wpdiscuz-sang-tieng-viet-218x108.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/dich-wpdiscuz-sang-tieng-viet-300x149.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/dich-wpdiscuz-sang-tieng-viet-700x347.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/dich-wpdiscuz-sang-tieng-viet-768x381.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/dich-wpdiscuz-sang-tieng-viet.png 1480w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>D\u00f9ng Phrase Setting \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ecbch wpDiscuz sang ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>T\u00f4i khuy\u1ebfn kh\u00edch b\u1ea1n n\u00ean d\u00f9ng c\u00e1ch n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ecbch thay v\u00ec ch\u1ec9nh s\u1eeda file PO (m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 file po c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ecbch m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n sang ti\u1ebfng Vi\u1ec7t) b\u1edfi v\u00ec Phrase Setting ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ee9a c\u00e1c string ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef c\u1ea7n d\u1ecbch m\u00e0 th\u00f4i. Trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ebb Email r\u1ea5t l\u00e0 quan tr\u1ecdng m\u00e0 t\u00f4i s\u1ebd tr\u00ecnh b\u00e0y \u1edf m\u1ee5c sau.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng t\u00ecm th\u1ea5y &#8220;Pharse setting&#8221; c\u1ee7a wpDiscuz v\u00ec b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh stick ch\u1ecdn v\u00e0o d\u00f9ng PO edit trong th\u1ebb general.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image is-style-default\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/dung-PO-de-dich-thuat.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"366\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/dung-PO-de-dich-thuat-1024x366.png\" alt=\"Dung Po De Dich Thuat\" class=\"wp-image-25388\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/dung-PO-de-dich-thuat-1024x366.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/dung-PO-de-dich-thuat-218x78.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/dung-PO-de-dich-thuat-300x107.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/dung-PO-de-dich-thuat-700x250.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/dung-PO-de-dich-thuat-768x275.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/dung-PO-de-dich-thuat.png 1894w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh stick ch\u1ecdn PO edit n\u00ean &#8220;Pharse Setting&#8221; s\u1ebd t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng \u1ea9n<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"pk-heading-numbered\">Qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd Subscription, c\u1ef1c quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a wpDiscuz<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>C\u01a1 ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ec3 wpDiscuz l\u01b0u tr\u1eef v\u00e0 qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd s\u1ebd d\u1ef1a theo WordPress user role, ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ecdc gi\u1ea3 khuy\u1ebfn kh\u00edch t\u1ea1o t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u0103ng nh\u1eadp v\u00e0 b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn tr\u00ean blog c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ec7 qu\u1ea3 c\u00f3 h\u1ea1i cho c\u1ea3 b\u1ea1n v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ecdc.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>WordPress users c\u1ee7a blog b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd ch\u1ee9a \u0111\u1ea7y c\u00e1c ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng subscriber kh\u00f4ng mong mu\u1ed1n v\u00e0 database ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng n\u1eb7ng h\u01a1n, c\u00e1i m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i g\u00ec. Ngo\u00e0i ra vi\u1ec7c l\u01b0u tr\u1eef th\u00f4ng tin ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady s\u1ebd ph\u1ea1m quy\u1ec1n ri\u00eang t\u01b0.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>V\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ecdc, h\u1ecd r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb block n\u1ebfu ch\u1eb3ng may b\u1ea1n stick v\u00e0o ch\u1eb7n &#8220;subscriber&#8221; nh\u01b0 b\u01b0\u1edbc #1 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i. Th\u00eam v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u0103ng nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn s\u1ebd l\u00e0m h\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m x\u00fac c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ecdc khi b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>C\u00e1ch t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 c\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ecdi b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn nh\u01b0 kh\u00e1ch (Guest)<\/strong>, ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i email v\u00e0 t\u00ean, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ecdc s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o ngay qua email m\u1ed7i khi b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ai \u0111\u00f3 tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ea1o t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n &#8220;subscriber&#8221; user.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image is-style-default\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/Cho-phep-Guests-binh-luan-o-form.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"488\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/Cho-phep-Guests-binh-luan-o-form-1024x488.png\" alt=\"Cho Phep Guests Binh Luan O Form\" class=\"wp-image-25405\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/Cho-phep-Guests-binh-luan-o-form-1024x488.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/Cho-phep-Guests-binh-luan-o-form-218x104.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/Cho-phep-Guests-binh-luan-o-form-300x143.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/Cho-phep-Guests-binh-luan-o-form-700x334.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/Cho-phep-Guests-binh-luan-o-form-768x366.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/Cho-phep-Guests-binh-luan-o-form.png 1521w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>B\u1eadt cho ph\u00e9p Guest b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn \u1edf Form<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image is-style-default\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/tat-chuc-nang-Social-Login.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"499\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/tat-chuc-nang-Social-Login-1024x499.png\" alt=\"Tat Chuc Nang Social Login\" class=\"wp-image-25404\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/tat-chuc-nang-Social-Login-1024x499.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/tat-chuc-nang-Social-Login-218x106.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/tat-chuc-nang-Social-Login-300x146.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/tat-chuc-nang-Social-Login-700x341.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/tat-chuc-nang-Social-Login-768x374.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/tat-chuc-nang-Social-Login.png 1682w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>T\u1eaft ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng Social Login \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh t\u1ea1o WordPress user t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ea1n g\u1eb7p l\u1ed7i kh\u00e1ch b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn email th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o khi b\u1ea1n tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn. C\u00f3 3 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn sau b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ch\u00fa \u00fd.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li><strong>C\u1ea5u h\u00ecnh SMTP ch\u01b0a \u0111\u00fang<\/strong>.: K\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 khi b\u1ea1n d\u00f9ng plugin SMTP cho WordPress th\u00ec t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n SMTP c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng, ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 t\u00ean mi\u1ec1n v\u00e0 email t\u00ean mi\u1ec1n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 v\u1edbi DKIM, DMARC, SPF, MX v\u00e0 \u0111ang \u1edf tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i &#8220;s\u1ee9c kho\u1ebb t\u1ed1t&#8221;, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng email s\u1ebd v\u1eabn v\u00e0o h\u1ed9p th\u01b0 Spam nh\u01b0 th\u01b0\u1eddng ho\u1eb7c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 g\u1eedi email \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<\/li><li><strong>Kh\u00f4ng b\u1eadt t\u00ednh n\u0103ng Reply Comment m\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ecbnh cho kh\u00e1ch b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn<\/strong>.: T\u00ednh n\u0103ng n\u00e0y s\u1ebd t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00eam theo d\u00f5i qua email m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n h\u1ecfi \u00fd ki\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn, n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng b\u1eadt cho kh\u00e1ch th\u00ec kh\u00e1ch s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn email th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o khi b\u1ea1n tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn.<\/li><li><strong>Kh\u00f4ng b\u1eadt ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng b\u1ecf qua x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn theo d\u00f5i<\/strong>.: T\u00ednh n\u0103ng n\u00e0y s\u1ebd t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng g\u1eedi email \u0111\u1ebfn kh\u00e1ch b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn v\u00e0 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u s\u1ef1 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn. N\u1ebfu kh\u00e1ch b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn ho\u1eb7c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y email th\u00ec \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng email tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn. C\u00e1ch t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 b\u1ea1n b\u1ecf qua b\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh r\u1ee7i ro.<\/li><\/ol>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image is-style-default\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/chuc-nang-theo-doi-cho-wpDiscuz.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"570\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/chuc-nang-theo-doi-cho-wpDiscuz-1024x570.png\" alt=\"Chuc Nang Theo Doi Cho Wpdiscuz\" class=\"wp-image-25402\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/chuc-nang-theo-doi-cho-wpDiscuz-1024x570.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/chuc-nang-theo-doi-cho-wpDiscuz-218x121.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/chuc-nang-theo-doi-cho-wpDiscuz-300x167.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/chuc-nang-theo-doi-cho-wpDiscuz-700x390.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/chuc-nang-theo-doi-cho-wpDiscuz-768x428.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/chuc-nang-theo-doi-cho-wpDiscuz.png 1471w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>Stick ch\u1ecdn 2 t\u00ednh n\u0103ng tr\u00ean s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o &#8220;Kh\u00e1ch&#8221; b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn lu\u00f4n nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c email th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o khi c\u00f3 ai \u0111\u00f3 tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>\u0110\u1ec3 ki\u1ec3m tra xem email c\u00f3 g\u1eedi \u0111\u00fang nh\u01b0 b\u1ea1n c\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t hay kh\u00f4ng th\u00ec b\u1ea1n n\u00ean d\u00f9ng plugin <strong>Post SMTP<\/strong>, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 plugin SMTP mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 t\u00f4i d\u00f9ng cho m\u1ecdi blog c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed-wordpress wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-plugin-directory\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<div class=\"suki-oembed\"><blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"xbE1KHiGXs\"><a href=\"https:\/\/vi.wordpress.org\/plugins\/post-smtp\/\">Post SMTP Mailer\/Email Log<\/a><\/blockquote><iframe title=\"&#8220;Post SMTP Mailer\/Email Log&#8221; &#8212; Plugin Directory\" class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\" src=\"https:\/\/vi.wordpress.org\/plugins\/post-smtp\/embed\/#?secret=xbE1KHiGXs\" data-secret=\"xbE1KHiGXs\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"><\/iframe><\/div>\n<\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Post SMTP c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng r\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi l\u00e0&nbsp;<strong>Email logs<\/strong> (t\u00ednh n\u0103ng n\u00e0y th\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 tr\u00ean c\u00e1c plugin tr\u1ea3 ph\u00ed). Truy c\u1eadp v\u00e0o Email logs b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ki\u1ec3m tra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ecbch s\u1eed email \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi cho kh\u00e1ch b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image is-style-default\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/email-log-cua-post-smtp.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"479\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/email-log-cua-post-smtp-1024x479.png\" alt=\"Email Log Cua Post Smtp\" class=\"wp-image-25393\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/email-log-cua-post-smtp-1024x479.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/email-log-cua-post-smtp-218x102.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/email-log-cua-post-smtp-300x140.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/email-log-cua-post-smtp-700x328.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/email-log-cua-post-smtp-768x359.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/email-log-cua-post-smtp.png 1626w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>Email Log c\u1ee7a plugin Post SMTP v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"tip\"><span class=\"title\">Ch\u00fa \u00dd<\/span>\n<p>T\u00ednh n\u0103ng \u0111\u0103ng nh\u1eadp b\u1eb1ng Social Login s\u1ebd t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ea1o WordPress subscriber user n\u00ean t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t h\u00e3y b\u1ecf t\u00ednh n\u0103ng n\u00e0y lu\u00f4n d\u00f9 n\u00f3 kh\u00e1 ti\u1ec7n l\u1ee3i.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"pk-heading-numbered\">H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn c\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t wpDiscuz gi\u00fap t\u1ed1i \u01b0u hi\u1ec7u su\u1ea5t ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a blog<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 m\u1eb9o h\u1eefu \u00edch sau \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap wpDiscuz ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng nh\u1eb9 h\u01a1n, tr\u01a1n tru h\u01a1n v\u00e0 nhanh h\u01a1n.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Disable AJAX WordPress.: Thay v\u00ec d\u00f9ng AJAX m\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a WordPress th\u00ec b\u1ea1n n\u00ean d\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a wpDiscuz s\u1ebd gi\u00fap ch\u1ea1y nhanh h\u01a1n.<\/li><li>Load script in footer.: T\u00f9y ch\u1ecdn n\u00e0y nh\u1eb1m h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf render block khi b\u1ea1n t\u1ea3i trang. Load n\u1ed9i dung \u0111\u1ea7u trang m\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u00e0 h\u01a1n.<\/li><li>Live Update m\u1ed7i 10 ph\u00fat.: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn n\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ed7i 10 ph\u00fat s\u1ebd gi\u1ea3m t\u1ea3i cho host.<\/li><li>Custom CSS style.: N\u00ean d\u00f9ng Custom CSS c\u1ee7a plugin wpDiscus thay v\u00ec ch\u1ec9nh CSS trong theme \u0111\u1ec3 CSS style ch\u1ec9 t\u1ea3i trong blog module thay v\u00ec to\u00e0n site.<\/li><li>Disable font awesome 5 n\u1ebfu theme \u0111\u00e3 t\u00edch h\u1ee3p s\u1eb5n.: N\u1ebfu theme b\u1ea1n \u0111ang d\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u00edch h\u1ee3p s\u1eb5n font awesome 5 th\u00ec b\u1ea1n h\u00e3y t\u1eaft tr\u00ean wpDiscuz.<\/li><li>Kh\u00f4ng d\u00f9ng Google reCapcha.: Google reCapcha s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1y th\u00eam script t\u1eeb Google g\u00e2y n\u1eb7ng th\u00eam cho trang. Thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 n\u00ean k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p d\u00f9ng plugin WPbruiser \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00e1ng spam hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 cho to\u00e0n site.<\/li><li>Gravatar cache.: B\u1eadt t\u00ednh n\u0103ng cache Gravatar v\u00e0 l\u01b0u cache l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 10 ng\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap t\u1ea3i b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn nhanh h\u01a1n.<\/li><li>Lazyload khu v\u1ef1c b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn.: B\u1eadt t\u00ednh n\u0103ng Lazyload s\u1ebd gi\u00fap c\u00e1c b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft t\u1ea3i trang nhanh h\u01a1n v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 t\u1ea3i b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn khi k\u00e9o xu\u1ed1ng cu\u1ed1i trang.<\/li><\/ol>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed-wordpress aligncenter wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-plugin-directory\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<div class=\"suki-oembed\"><blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"HCBMjCioVC\"><a href=\"https:\/\/vi.wordpress.org\/plugins\/goodbye-captcha\/\">WPBruiser {no- Captcha anti-Spam}<\/a><\/blockquote><iframe title=\"&#8220;WPBruiser {no- Captcha anti-Spam}&#8221; &#8212; Plugin Directory\" class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\" src=\"https:\/\/vi.wordpress.org\/plugins\/goodbye-captcha\/embed\/#?secret=HCBMjCioVC\" data-secret=\"HCBMjCioVC\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"><\/iframe><\/div>\n<\/div><figcaption>N\u00ean d\u00f9ng WPBruiser \u0111\u1ec3 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p ch\u1ed1ng Spam hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n, kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n Google reCapcha<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-style-default\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/CSS-cho-wpDiscuz.p